But they managed the situation properly and retained beneficial results even if they were lower than they had before the crisis.
However, at Farmet, they continued to invest uncompromisingly in research and development.
"We have built a training and research center with the resources, strengthened the company's presentation at international exhibitions and won major awards at national exhibitions," Zdarsky said.
Everything leaves us thinking that the crisis is behind them.
The numbers are rising, and with them the number of employees.
"To the new winner I wish this pleasant feeling of victory but in a calm atmosphere," says Karel Zdarsky.
