Pakistan's nuclear program raises concern in the United States
Islamabad is producing nuclear weapons at "a faster pace than any other country."
WikiLeaks filters confirm the connection between the Taliban and Pakistan.
The content of the correspondence between the U.S. Embassy in Pakistan and the U.S. State Department filtered by the Wikileaks portal confirms the huge concerns that the Pakistani nuclear program raises in Washington.
